2a:["$","p",null,{"children":"As UI systems mature and spread across a company, the requirement for them to be able to work with new technologies and frameworks will only increase. Whether design tokens as a tool are the answer to this or not, the concept of thinking about components as compositions of these tokens will still hold true."}]
